{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 1590822, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "jayroo79", "body": "He's much older than he looks.", "date": "2011-12-05T18:52:24-06:00", "rating": 13, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "And while he can be a damn scary gnome, he's also so fiercely protective of his people and cares so much for them (else he wouldn't BE that protective) that they continue to hang around the Faire after death! Don't believe me? Well--if you miss the water after being shot from the cannon, you'll meet a few of these people. Silas may be an eerie little cuss, but he's awesome just the same.", "creationdate": "2012-05-16T20:39:12-05:00", "id": 544037, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1590822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "MiltiadesBooga", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Older that he looks, no kidding. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=56050]Brendon[/url] says he escaped from Strom and met Silas... but Strom stopped existing *centuries* ago. Whoever Silas is, he is not a normal gnome.", "creationdate": "2012-12-13T13:17:05-06:00", "id": 611323, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1590822, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
